# Accounts

## [Ispras]

IMAPStore ispras-remote
Host mail.ispras.ru
User shishqa@ispras.ru
PassCmd "pass show ispras/mail"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore ispras-local
Path /mnt/WorkDisk/share/mail/ispras/
Inbox /mnt/WorkDisk/share/mail/ispras/inbox/

Channel ispras-inbox
Far :ispras-remote:"INBOX"
Near :ispras-local:inbox
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel ispras-sent
Far :ispras-remote:"Sent"
Near :ispras-local:sent
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel ispras-spam
Far :ispras-remote:"Spam"
Near :ispras-local:spam
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel ispras-trash
Far :ispras-remote:"Trash"
Near :ispras-local:trash
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group ispras
Channel ispras-inbox
Channel ispras-sent
Channel ispras-spam
Channel ispras-trash

## [shishqa.main@gmail.com]

IMAPStore shishqa-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
User shishqa.main@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show neomutt/shishqa.main@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore shishqa-local
Path /mnt/WorkDisk/share/mail/personal/shishqa.main/
Inbox /mnt/WorkDisk/share/mail/personal/shishqa.main/inbox/

Channel shishqa-inbox
Far :shishqa-remote:"INBOX"
Near :shishqa-local:inbox
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel shishqa-sent
Far :shishqa-remote:"[Gmail]/&BB4EQgQ,BEAEMAQyBDsENQQ9BD0ESwQ1-"
Near :shishqa-local:sent
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel shishqa-drafts
Far :shishqa-remote:"[Gmail]/&BCcENQRABD0EPgQyBDgEOgQ4-"
Near :shishqa-local:drafts
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel shishqa-spam
Far :shishqa-remote:"[Gmail]/&BCEEPwQwBDw-"
Near :shishqa-local:spam
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel shishqa-trash
Far :shishqa-remote:"[Gmail]/&BBoEPgRABDcEOAQ9BDA-"
